---
/**
 * STRIDEVisual.astro
 * STRIDE threat modeling methodology
 */
---

<div class="stv-wrap">
  <h3 class="stv-title">STRIDE Threat Categories</h3>
  <div class="stv-grid">
    <div class="stv-cat" style="--i:0;--c:#ef4444;">
      <div class="stv-letter">S</div>
      <div class="stv-info">
        <div class="stv-name">Spoofing</div>
        <div class="stv-desc">Pretending to be someone else. Fake credentials, session hijacking, IP spoofing.</div>
        <div class="stv-fix">MFA, mutual TLS, token validation</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stv-cat" style="--i:1;--c:#f59e0b;">
      <div class="stv-letter">T</div>
      <div class="stv-info">
        <div class="stv-name">Tampering</div>
        <div class="stv-desc">Modifying data in transit or at rest. SQL injection, man-in-the-middle, altered configs.</div>
        <div class="stv-fix">Input validation, HMAC signatures, TLS</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stv-cat" style="--i:2;--c:#818cf8;">
      <div class="stv-letter">R</div>
      <div class="stv-info">
        <div class="stv-name">Repudiation</div>
        <div class="stv-desc">Denying an action occurred. No audit trail, unsigned transactions.</div>
        <div class="stv-fix">Audit logging, digital signatures, timestamps</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stv-cat" style="--i:3;--c:#06b6d4;">
      <div class="stv-letter">I</div>
      <div class="stv-info">
        <div class="stv-name">Information Disclosure</div>
        <div class="stv-desc">Exposing data to unauthorized parties. Verbose errors, missing encryption, leaky APIs.</div>
        <div class="stv-fix">Encryption, access controls, error handling</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stv-cat" style="--i:4;--c:#4ade80;">
      <div class="stv-letter">D</div>
      <div class="stv-info">
        <div class="stv-name">Denial of Service</div>
        <div class="stv-desc">Making the system unavailable. Resource exhaustion, amplification attacks.</div>
        <div class="stv-fix">Rate limiting, auto-scaling, WAF rules</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stv-cat" style="--i:5;--c:#f472b6;">
      <div class="stv-letter">E</div>
      <div class="stv-info">
        <div class="stv-name">Elevation of Privilege</div>
        <div class="stv-desc">Gaining unauthorized access levels. IDOR, privilege escalation, broken authz.</div>
        <div class="stv-fix">Least privilege, RBAC, authorization checks</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .stv-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border:1px solid #334155;border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0}
  .stv-title{color:#f1f5f9;text-align:center;font-size:1.25rem;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .stv-grid{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.6rem}
  .stv-cat{display:flex;gap:.75rem;align-items:flex-start;background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border-radius:10px;padding:.8rem;opacity:0;animation:stvSlide .35s ease forwards;animation-delay:calc(var(--i)*.1s)}
  @keyframes stvSlide{from{opacity:0;transform:translateX(-12px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0)}}
  .stv-letter{background:var(--c);color:#0f172a;width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:900;font-size:1rem;flex-shrink:0}
  .stv-info{flex:1}
  .stv-name{color:var(--c);font-weight:700;font-size:.82rem;margin-bottom:.15rem}
  .stv-desc{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.72rem;margin-bottom:.2rem}
  .stv-fix{color:#64748b;font-size:.65rem;font-style:italic}
</style>
